<!-- DEDICATION -->
<section id="dedication" data-reveal>
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="dedication-content">
      <div class="section-label">Dedication</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">In Memory of My Father</h2>
      <div class="section-divider" style="margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;"></div>
      <div class="dedication-photo">
        <img src="/images/papa2.1.jpg" alt="The author's father, educator and lifelong mentor" loading="lazy">
        
      </div>
      <p class="dedication-text">To my beloved father and mentor, who departed from our world on September 29, 2025. With your passing, the world lost a great man who gave his life to the noblest of missions: the education of generations. From the playing fields of schoolyards to university lecture halls, you built minds as you built bodies, holding fast to the belief that physical discipline is the foundation upon which the discipline of thought is raised.</p>
      <p class="dedication-text">Your journey&mdash;from devoted teacher to leader in the highest ranks of public service&mdash;was a living testament to your integrity, your foresight, and your unshakeable faith in what education can do. Even after retirement, your heart remained with children. You wrote stories for them that ignited their imaginations and opened the doors of dreaming.</p>
      <p class="dedication-name">Teacher. Leader. Traveler. Storyteller.</p>
      <p class="dedication-dates">d. September 29, 2025</p>
      <p class="dedication-note">This book is but a humble attempt to continue the circle of learning that he began.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

